These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, van, motorbike, trike
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, blend, old-henry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, sunflower, marigold
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, puzzles, skydiving, dancing
 1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the old-henry-smoker##2
10. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the blend-smoker is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | motorbike  | scooter    | trike    | van   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster     | prince   | blend       | old-henry    |
| Flower   | begonia | rose | marigold    | sunflower |
| Hobby           | puzzles | dancing       | woodworking | skydiving     |

