.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, june, april, march
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, baccarat, siglo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, folk, house, rock
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, 7up, tea
 1. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
 2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of indie##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 9. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of house is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday          | november  | june    | april     | march       |
| Cigar         | baccarat | siglo | davidoff   | prince |
| Music-Genre   | house | indie   | folk   | rock    |
| Beverage         | 7up | tea  | milk | juice   |

