.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, techno, metal, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, jet-ski, motorbike
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, bridge, go
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, mauve, amber, chestnut
 1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 2. the person playing domino is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the fan of techno is the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is the person playing go##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
 9. the fan of metal is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person who likes emerald is the fan of metal##1
11. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | r&b | metal   | trance    | techno      |
| Transport           | jet-ski | quad-bike | roller | motorbike     |
| Game   | domino      | go   | scrabble   | bridge |
| Color           | chestnut         | emerald       | amber  | mauve       |

