.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, september, december
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, country, indie, soul
House: gothic-revival, modern, cottage, art-deco
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, accountant, security-guard
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of jazz##1
 2. the cottage house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 4. the modern house is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the security-guard##1
 6. the accountant is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the accountant##1
 8. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 9. the accountant is the modern house##1
10. the dressmaker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of soul##1
12. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | december       | september   | april   | october   |
| Music-Genre       | country        | soul | jazz    | indie       |
| House      | art-deco | modern    | cottage  | gothic-revival |
| Job      | journalist  | accountant  | dressmaker | security-guard    |

