.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
House: wooden, modern, palace, townhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, german, spanish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, folk, d&b, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, cain, blend
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the german is between the prince-smoker and the townhouse house##2
 3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the fan of folk is the wooden house##1
 5. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 6. the french is in an even position##4
 7. the modern house is the fan of house##1
 8. the german is the fan of folk##1
 9. the wooden house is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
10. the fan of folk is on the right of the spanish##1
11. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the palace house##3
12. the spanish is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| House    | palace    | townhouse      | wooden          | modern    |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish       | german | french |
| Music-Genre     | techno     | d&b      | folk     | house |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | blend | cain        | prince   |

