.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, soccer, weightlifting
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, hedgehog, dog
House: wooden, palace, cape-cod, farmhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, collecting, gardening
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
 6. the farmhouse house is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the palace house##2
 7. the cape-cod house is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Sport      | soccer  | basketball    | volleyball       | weightlifting       |
| Pet          | dog    | hedgehog | turtle | ferret     |
| House   | wooden | cape-cod        | farmhouse    | palace   |
| Hobby   | drawing  | collecting      | gardening    | woodworking |

