 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 9. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
