.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, blues, reggae, funk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, rose, daffodil, iris
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, airplane, car, roller
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, lemonade, coffee
 1. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking lemonade##2
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person drinking tea is between the person driving the trike and the person who growsrose##2
10. the fan of blues is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
12. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | blues  | reggae    | rock    | funk |
| Flower   | daffodil   | aconite       | rose  | iris    |
| Transport   | trike | airplane | car | roller   |
| Beverage           | lemonade    | tea        | coffee   | mirinda    |

