.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, guinea-pig, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, december, april
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, mirinda, almond-milk
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, scrabble, snooker
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Pet          | frog     | guinea-pig      | rat  | hamster        |
| Birthday   | may     | december | september | april      |
| Beverage   | coffee      | fanta        | almond-milk        | mirinda        |
| Game         | snooker | canasta    | mah-jongg      | scrabble |

