 3. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsbegonia is between the person eating spinach and the person who growsazalea##2
 5. the person eating cranberry is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsazalea##2
 6. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
 7. the photographer is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 8. the dancer is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 9. the lawyer is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
10. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre      | r&b   | salsa   | dubstep     | punk   |
| Flower   | rose  | begonia       | azalea | amaryllis |
| Food           | spinach     | cranberry   | garlic     | peach     |
| Job         | fisherman | lawyer | dancer   | photographer |

