.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, russian, dutch, argentine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, may, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, jet-ski, airplane
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, pall-mall, swisher
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the russian##3
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the argentine##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
11. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in august is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality      | dutch       | russian | thai        | argentine        |
| Birthday         | july | may       | august | september |
| Transport   | airplane     | skateboard        | trike    | jet-ski      |
| Cigar         | aristoff     | pall-mall    | swisher | bolivar   |

