.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, siglo, old-henry, oliveros
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, fisherman, lawyer, dressmaker
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, go, bridge
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lilac, orange, apricot
 1. the oliveros-smoker is the person playing go##1
 2. the person playing go is between the doctor and the dressmaker##2
 3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the fisherman##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
 8. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
10. the doctor is in an even position##4
11. the doctor is on the far right##1
12. the prince-smoker is on the right of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | siglo      | prince | oliveros     | old-henry        |
| Job   | lawyer | dressmaker  | fisherman     | doctor |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | poker | go      | bridge |
| Color     | apricot | lilac     | orange | red       |

 